              DIGITAL LEGACIES
            </span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="font-sans text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Our website design development services ensure that you get high quality and Genuine website Designing services for an extremely cost effective prices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Premium Founder Section -->
    <section class="py-10 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-system">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Main Founder Card -->
            <div class="relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 items-center">
                <!-- Founder Avatar -->
                <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
                  <div class="relative inline-block group">
                    <div class="w-64 h-64 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
                      <img src="/images/anilprofile.jpg" alt="Founder" class="w-64 h-64 rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-xl" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 bg-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                      <span class="text-white text-xs">‚≠ê</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Founder Info -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 text-left">
                  <div class="mb-6">
                    <h3 class="font-grotesk text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                      Anil Gaikwad
                    </h3>
                    <p class="font-grotesk text-xl text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 font-medium">
                      Founder & Web Developer
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">I am Anil, the founder of Evolve Web Solapur. With a Master of Computer Applications and a strong passion for creating user-focused digital experiences, I started Evolve Web to help businesses build a meaningful online presence. My goal is to make high-quality web design and development accessible, while also sharing my knowledge through Java classes so that anyone interested in learning can grow with confidence.</p>
                  
                  <blockquote class="font-sans text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 italic border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4 mb-6">
                    "I believe that every website should be a masterpiece - fast, accessible, beautiful, 
                    and perfectly aligned with your business goals."
                  </blockquote>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Background Elements -->
            <div class="absolute -z-10 top-8 -left-8 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute -z-10 bottom-8 -right-8 w-20 h-20 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

     <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="py-20 sm:py-32 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-system">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-left sm:text-center mb-16 sm:mb-24">
            <h2 class="font-grotesk text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              OUR STORY
            </h2>
            <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">The Evolve Web Solapur is the top website design company in Solapur who provides more than website design and development. The Evolve Web Technology will produce a custom website design that will maintain the professional image that you've worked hard to build. </p>
            <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">If you have not yet to take your business website on the web, Evolve Web Solapur take responsibility to improve your business and develop your website upto live on web (Evolve Web Solapur | One of The Best Web Designing companies in Solapur, who provides the services to make it successful with minimum maintanance cost. Evolve Web Solapur offers the top and best quality web designing services with best afforts.</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Drive traffic, generate leads, boost your sales, and build your brand by hiring our powerful digital marketing services. Our impactful campaigns run with cutting-edge strategies, innovative ideas.</p>
            <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Our company is one and only one the most affordable prices, creative and reliable professional Website Designing, Java Training, Digital Marketing and PPT Presentation Designing available in Solapur, Maharashtra. Evolve Web Solapur understand the needs of our clients/customers, and we provide listed services at affordable prices.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="py-20 sm:py-32 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-system">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-24">
          <h2 class="font-grotesk text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
            OUR VALUES
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
            The principles that guide everything we do and define who we are.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          {[
            {
              icon: "üíé",
              title: "Excellence",
              description: "We never settle for good enough. Every project is an opportunity to create something extraordinary.",
              color: "from-blue-500 to-cyan-600"
            },
            {
              icon: "üöÄ",
              title: "Innovation",
              description: "We embrace cutting-edge technologies and creative solutions to stay ahead of the curve.",
              color: "from-purple-500 to-pink-600"
            },
            {
              icon: "ü§ù",
              title: "Partnership",
              description: "We work collaboratively with our clients, treating their goals as our own.",
              color: "from-green-500 to-emerald-600"
            },
            {
              icon: "‚ö°",
              title: "Performance",
              description: "We optimize every aspect for speed, accessibility, and exceptional user experience.",
              color: "from-orange-500 to-red-600"
            }
          ].map((value) => (
            <div class="group text-center">
              <div class={`w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br ${value.color} rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500`}>
                <span class="text-2xl text-white">{value.icon}</span>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="font-grotesk text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
                {value.title}
              </h3>
              
              <p class="font-sans text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                {value.description}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="py-20 sm:py-32 bg-gray-300 relative overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Animated Background -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse delay-1000"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:grid-system relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="font-grotesk text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
            READY TO CREATE TOGETHER?
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-xl text-black mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Let's join forces to build something remarkable that stands the test of time.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center font-grotesk font-bold bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl">
              Start Your Journey
              <span class="ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">‚ú®</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/work" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center font-grotesk font-medium border-2 border-black/30 text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-sm">
              See Our Work
              <span class="ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">‚Üí</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />

</BaseLayout>

